summary:
— Experienced software engineer (8+ years) with a solid background in a wide range of software development aspects in different business contexts throughout an entire software development lifecycle, including coding standards, code reviews, source control management, build processes, testing, and operations.
— Experienced in banking, financial, medical and telecommunication solutions. 
— Develops software solutions by analyzing the giving information, conferring with users, studying systems flow, data usage, and work processes.
— Have an adequate knowledge of web related technologies (Web applications, Web Services and Service Oriented Architectures) and of network/web related protocols. In addition to experience with RESTful Services and APIs
— Experienced dealing with large scale desktop systems.
— Have Deep understanding for Algorithms and DS 
— Familiar with Agile practices and Scrum master experience.
— Have a deep understanding for cloud computing concepts with proven experience in AWS.
— Excellent communication skills proven through customer interactions by building strong client
engagements, resolving conflicts and managing strategic plans.
— Self-motivated, clear structured working style, high quality standards.
—Experienced in Coaching and teaching computer science students and Juniors gained by working as a Teaching assistant at  Helwan University.
